Attack of the PETSCII Robots C++
================================
Work in progress

SDL version
-----------
brew install sdl2 sdl2_image
make
./petrobots

Amiga version
-------------
smake
petrobots

Amiga memory requirements
-------------------------
32000  CHIP always: main screen
98304  CHIP always: tiles
24576  CHIP always: sprites
4      CHIP always: generic tile mask
6144   CHIP always: masks for tiles with transparency
24576  CHIP always: masks for sprites
120    CHIP always: cursor sprite left
120    CHIP always: cursor sprite right
576    CHIP always: faces
4608   CHIP always: item graphics
8064   CHIP always: health graphics
105804 CHIP always: module
2108   CHIP always: sound fx module
11228  CHIP always: sounds_dsbarexp.raw
18184  CHIP always: sounds_dsdoropn.raw
4512   CHIP always: sounds_dsgetpow.raw
2204   CHIP always: sounds_dsitemup.raw
4264   CHIP always: sounds_dsoof.raw
5512   CHIP always: sounds_dspistol.raw
14284  CHIP always: sounds_dsplasma.raw
8928   CHIP always: sounds_dsplpain.raw
4264   CHIP always: sounds_dsswtchx.raw
5732   CHIP always: sounds_dswpnup.raw
2      CHIP always: SquareWave.raw
2000   FAST always: PET screen memory address -> Amiga bitplane address mapping
256    FAST always: offsets to masks for tiles with transparency
256    FAST always: offsets to sprites for sprite tiles
1024   FAST always: C64 font
14351  FAST always: intro screen
1333   FAST always: game screen
105804 CHIP on-demand: mod.get psyched
17182  CHIP on-demand: mod.lose
66438  CHIP on-demand: mod.metal heads
71738  CHIP on-demand: mod.metallic bop amiga
99498  CHIP on-demand: mod.robot attack
88656  CHIP on-demand: mod.rushin in
34098  CHIP on-demand: mod.win

